    "Meanwhile, the lexical complexity metric showed that the proportion of academic vocabulary increased from 8.3 to 22.1%, with the accurate use of high-frequency academic terms such as \"mitigate\" and \"sustainable. \"",
    "This study conducts systematic ablation experiments to assess the synergistic effects of the multidimensional feedback modules.",
    "In Table 6, disabling specific modules-such as Grammar Correction (GC), Lexical Optimization (LO), Sentence Diversity (SD), and Content Coherence (CC)-resulted in a gradual decline in",
